<li><strong>Oral antibiotics:</strong> <a href="https:///generics/clindamycin-209621?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Folliculitis_factbox_0_treatment_5_direct_link_1">Clindamycin</a>, Cephalexin, <a href="https:///generics/dicloxacillin-209718?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Folliculitis_factbox_0_treatment_5_direct_link_2">Dicloxacillin</a>, <a href="https:///generics/ampicillin-209373?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Folliculitis_factbox_0_treatment_5_direct_link_3">Ampicillin</a>, <a href="https:///generics/trimethoprim-210868?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Folliculitis_factbox_0_treatment_5_direct_link_4">Trimethoprim</a>-<a href="https:///generics/sulfamethoxazole-210764?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Folliculitis_factbox_0_treatment_5_direct_link_5">sulfamethoxazole</a>, or <a href="https:///generics/ciprofloxacin-209606?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Folliculitis_factbox_0_treatment_5_direct_link_6">Ciprofloxacin</a></li>
